WEBVTT

00:00.924 --> 00:02.734
<i>Previously on</i>
"The Path"...

00:02.819 --> 00:04.951
This is my resort property

00:05.031 --> 00:06.085
on Kuta Beach.

00:06.162 --> 00:07.673
I would like to convert it

00:07.742 --> 00:10.148
into the first Meyerist Center
in Asia.

00:10.273 --> 00:11.839
To the Light in Bali.

00:11.924 --> 00:14.059
He wants me to take things
over for a couple of days.

00:14.091 --> 00:16.388
Okay, but you're still gonna
make it to Washington, right?

00:16.456 --> 00:17.932
No, actually no. No, I can't.

00:18.009 --> 00:19.351
What the fuck is wrong
with you?

00:19.428 --> 00:21.021
A waitress from
a women's rights dinner.

00:21.090 --> 00:22.830
- What are you doing here?
- So nice to meet you.

00:22.899 --> 00:24.668
Thanks for supporting
a woman's right to choose.

00:24.737 --> 00:26.088
Let's get the vote out
in November.

00:26.157 --> 00:27.581
Something happened, Cal.

00:27.658 --> 00:29.501
- Happened?
- To you.

00:29.578 --> 00:31.346
With Steve.

00:31.423 --> 00:33.975
- How did...
- You don't have to tell me.

00:34.052 --> 00:36.139
We are looking at
the very first draft of Ladder,

00:36.216 --> 00:37.400
and I believe that

00:37.477 --> 00:39.103
there's a second author.
Lilith.

00:39.180 --> 00:40.948
She believes that Eddie
will die.

00:41.025 --> 00:42.903
- Why?
- The Movement will crumble

00:42.980 --> 00:45.457
without Eddie, and the world
will crumble

00:45.534 --> 00:47.203
without The Movement.
Where is she?

00:47.280 --> 00:49.131
I just knew you'd
find me.

00:49.208 --> 00:51.754
You never told me that Vera
was your daughter.

00:51.831 --> 00:53.222
Vera put me in here,

00:53.299 --> 00:55.310
and she's the only one
who can get me out.

00:55.387 --> 00:57.181
I think you're right
where you need to be.

00:57.258 --> 00:58.768
Sarah!

