to please not contact us again.

24:44.861 --> 24:46.837
Please, help me.

24:46.914 --> 24:48.541
I'm extremely confused.

24:50.463 --> 24:52.549
I'm guessing that's
your lawyer.

24:52.626 --> 24:55.180
