26:20.851 --> 26:22.989
No, I don't want to hear
what he has to say about us.

26:23.057 --> 26:26.194
It's not what he said.
It's what you said.

26:26.271 --> 26:28.157
Mm.

26:33.961 --> 26:36.507
"Every moment of my life,
my childhood,

26:36.584 --> 26:39.513
the pain has all been
worth it."

26:39.590 --> 26:41.349
God, I was corny.

26:41.426 --> 26:43.069
No.

26:43.146 --> 26:45.066
I love it.

26:47.447 --> 26:49.366
"Because it led me to you."

26:51.830 --> 26:53.916
You are kind.

26:53.993 --> 26:56.464
You are beautiful.

26:56.541 --> 26:58.559
You are Light.

26:58.636 --> 27:01.642
You have shown me
what love is.

27:04.814 --> 27:08.236
I wish I was still
that person for you.

27:08.313 --> 27:10.116
Hey.

27:12.497 --> 27:15.342
You still are.
No.

27:15.419 --> 27:17.930
- Yes.
- I'm not.

27:18.007 --> 27:20.261
Just in a different way.

27:26.942 --> 27:28.319
Hey, Vera.

27:29.614 --> 27:33.337
Oh, so, this is what
you're caught up with?

27:33.414 --> 27:36.252
- Vera.
- I have nothing to say to you.

27:38.882 --> 27:41.720
There's an entire Movement
out there depending on you.

27:41.797 --> 27:44.107
People who believe in you.

27:44.184 --> 27:47.356
Counting on you,
and you're in here...

27:47.433 --> 27:50.579
Reading a bunch
of Steve's shit!

27:50.656 --> 27:51.998
With a woman who sold you out

27:52.075 --> 27:53.661
to a safety school college
professor.

27:53.738 --> 27:56.792
- That's enough.
- No, it isn't.

27:56.869 --> 27:58.929
Eddie, I believe in you.

27:59.014 --> 28:00.998
I believe in this Movement.

28:01.067 --> 28:03.371
I would destroy my life for it.

28:03.465 --> 28:05.177
I would destroy everything
I've worked

28:05.246 --> 28:06.873
so fucking hard
to put behind me.

28:06.949 --> 28:09.029
- What are you talking about?
- You should be out there

28:09.098 --> 28:11.585
fighting for us instead
of hiding in here with...

28:12.028 --> 28:14.202
someone who doesn't believe
in it, or you.

28:14.279 --> 28:16.415
Hey.

28:19.422 --> 28:22.427
♪♪

28:25.434 --> 28:27.778
♪♪

28:27.855 --> 28:29.190
Should we head back
to Forest?

28:29.267 --> 28:31.319
Yeah, in a minute.

28:31.396 --> 28:35.370
It's so beautiful.
Yeah, it is.

28:45.474 --> 28:47.602
I need to tell you something.

28:49.356 --> 28:52.076
It's just like
I stole their music.

28:52.153 --> 28:54.116
- What do you need to tell me?
- Uh...

28:56.538 --> 28:58.590
Ah, I, um...

28:58.667 --> 29:01.971
Maybe I'm not clear enough,
um...

29:02.048 --> 29:03.718
I love you.
I know.

29:03.795 --> 29:06.849
No, no, no. No.
No, okay, Mary...

29:06.926 --> 29:10.196
I love you.

29:10.273 --> 29:12.868
And, um...

29:12.945 --> 29:17.829
I wanted to come out here today
to the city because, uh...

29:17.906 --> 29:23.591
My parents and the compound
and all the Steve stuff...

29:23.668 --> 29:26.479
It's the past.

29:26.556 --> 29:28.809
You are my future.

29:28.886 --> 29:31.607
You and Forest.

29:35.616 --> 29:40.465
I... I thought of us as married
for a long time, but...

29:40.542 --> 29:43.757
you deserve to have a ring
on your finger.

29:45.301 --> 29:48.516
I mean, you deserve everything.

29:48.593 --> 29:52.155
I want to give it to you.

29:52.232 --> 29:55.988
I will try to give it to you.

29:56.065 --> 29:58.869
So, uh...

30:00.666 --> 30:03.260
Mary Cox,

30:03.337 --> 30:05.173
will you marry me?

30:05.250 --> 30:07.261
- Really?
- Yeah.

30:07.338 --> 30:09.850
Well, um.

30:09.927 --> 30:11.736
I mean.

30:11.813 --> 30:13.072
Wow, um.

30:13.149 --> 30:14.970
Okay, so I'll take the job,

30:15.040 --> 30:16.192
- and we'll figure out the next steps.
- Yeah.

30:16.261 --> 30:17.612
- And we'll start.
- Yeah.

30:17.681 --> 30:19.326
Yeah, I mean I'll still be
with Meyerism.

30:19.403 --> 30:21.372
But you won't do the TV show?

30:21.449 --> 30:23.711
Yeah, yeah, but with you
at my side.

30:25.466 --> 30:27.469
Is that why you're doing
this?

30:27.546 --> 30:31.233
- No, no. No, that's not why.
- Cal.

30:31.310 --> 30:33.647
I supported you,
and I followed you

30:33.724 --> 30:36.828
wherever you needed
to be, but...

30:36.905 --> 30:40.912
You won't get better
unless you leave this place.

30:40.989 --> 30:43.516
And, um...

30:43.711 --> 30:46.836
If you don't get better,

30:47.231 --> 30:49.994
I can't love you.

30:51.601 --> 30:53.778
♪♪

30:53.855 --> 30:56.275
You're wrong
because I'm working on myself,

30:56.352 --> 30:58.656
and I'm in therapy.
I'm in secular therapy.

30:58.733 --> 31:01.544
All right?
And I'm making progress.

31:01.621 --> 31:04.257
You'll never leave him.
Or Meyerism, will you?

31:04.334 --> 31:05.886
And you know
how fucked up that is?

31:05.963 --> 31:07.841
No, no, but I don't need
to leave Meyerism.

31:07.918 --> 31:09.218
I need to take it back
from him,

31:09.295 --> 31:10.972
and that is what I'm doing.

31:11.049 --> 31:12.810
Okay?

31:16.024 --> 31:18.112
I'm gonna take the job.

31:35.772 --> 31:36.941
Empirical evidence.

31:39.112 --> 31:42.076
Who has read Professor Neill's
article?

31:44.749 --> 31:45.918
Be honest.

31:47.546 --> 31:49.348
Great.

31:49.425 --> 31:52.521
We are going to unburden with
any questions and concerns.

31:52.598 --> 31:54.224
We don't have to do this,
Hawk.

31:54.301 --> 31:56.021
Yes, we do.

31:58.108 --> 32:01.364
Because in this Movement we do
not oppose critical thinking.

32:01.441 --> 32:03.202
Could you hit the light,
please?

32:05.666 --> 32:09.722
Which, by the way,
is the first sign

32:09.799 --> 32:11.559
that you're in a cult

32:11.636 --> 32:14.642
according to the American
Psychiatric Association.

32:16.186 --> 32:19.024
Monica. Do we "dishonor
the family unit"?

32:19.101 --> 32:21.370
- Um, no.
- No.

32:21.447 --> 32:24.243
If I recall correctly,
my dad actually encouraged you

32:24.320 --> 32:27.083
to be loyal to your family
instead of The Movement.

32:30.465 --> 32:32.760
Do we penalize members
for leaving?

32:32.837 --> 32:35.857
No.
No, Cal left, and he's back.

32:35.934 --> 32:40.025
My dad left, and now he's
The Guardian of the Light.

32:40.102 --> 32:43.038
So, no. Cross that off.
Not a cult.

32:43.115 --> 32:44.492
Hawk. We get it.

32:44.569 --> 32:46.328
No, we're doing this.

32:46.405 --> 32:49.760
Garth, do we put down other
churches and groups?

32:49.837 --> 32:51.806
- No, not that I know of.
- Right.

32:51.883 --> 32:53.469
I dated someone
from another faith.

32:53.546 --> 32:56.231
I fucking loved someone
from another faith.

32:56.308 --> 32:58.771
"Do you feel like something
is being hidden from you?"

32:58.848 --> 32:59.905
No.
No.

32:59.982 --> 33:01.492
We are transparent.

33:01.569 --> 33:04.073
"Are you told not to question
what is taught?"

33:04.150 --> 33:05.409
No.
No, you can ask

33:05.486 --> 33:07.379
any question, any time.

33:07.456 --> 33:08.957
"Are you made to feel
like a failure?"

33:09.034 --> 33:10.760
No.

33:10.837 --> 33:12.339
"Do you feel like you have
no home

33:12.416 --> 33:13.675
outside of The Movement?"

33:13.752 --> 33:15.679
No.
Great, so you guys get it.

33:15.756 --> 33:19.521
Now, do you have any questions
or concerns?

33:19.598 --> 33:21.357
No!

33:33.340 --> 33:35.177
‐

33:40.187 --> 33:43.945
- Right this way, Mr. Roberts.
- Okay. All right, thank you.

33:49.707 --> 33:52.044
- You're right here.
- Thank you.

34:11.583 --> 34:14.213
Look, I'm about to go on TV.
I can't talk now.

34:14.290 --> 34:15.882
I'm the mole.

34:15.960 --> 34:17.476
What?

34:17.554 --> 34:19.514
I'm the student who talked
