34:29.946 --> 34:32.542
- And I slept with him.
- Fuck, Sarah.

34:35.005 --> 34:36.675
What do you want me to do
with this?

34:36.752 --> 34:38.603
I want you to use it.

34:38.679 --> 34:41.016
Do whatever you want.
Use my name, I don't care.

34:41.092 --> 34:43.188
I want you to crush him.

34:53.083 --> 34:56.130
All right, everyone,
we're going up in five.

35:00.347 --> 35:02.142
Mr. Roberts, Professor Neill

35:02.219 --> 35:04.354
called Meyerism
"controversial"...

35:04.431 --> 35:06.074
And... and a cult.

35:06.151 --> 35:09.080
That's okay, Ruben, I'm not
afraid of the "c" word.

35:09.157 --> 35:10.951
I've been a part of
The Movement

35:11.028 --> 35:12.420
almost my whole life,

35:12.497 --> 35:14.090
and I've seen people
come and go

35:14.167 --> 35:16.003
because contrary to what
you might believe,

35:16.080 --> 35:17.389
our doors are open.

35:17.466 --> 35:18.842
In fact, I myself left

35:18.919 --> 35:20.596
for a time, but I came back

35:20.673 --> 35:23.442
because I believe
in Eddie Lane.

35:23.519 --> 35:26.574
And I can assure you, he's not
the megalomaniacal monster

35:26.651 --> 35:27.985
you described in the article.

35:28.062 --> 35:29.580
He's a real person.
A humble person.

35:29.657 --> 35:30.958
He didn't seem like a real
and humble person

35:31.026 --> 35:31.951
when he showed up at my house

35:32.028 --> 35:33.546
in the middle of the night

35:33.623 --> 35:35.300
and called me ignorant and
physically threatened me.

35:35.368 --> 35:36.635
‐
You threatened him?

35:36.712 --> 35:38.556
I told him to stay away
from my wife.

35:38.633 --> 35:40.395
Maybe you should have said
something to Cal.

35:40.463 --> 35:42.222
- - No, he's okay.
- Like I said,

35:42.299 --> 35:45.311
Eddie Lane is a real person
with flaws and a temper.

35:45.388 --> 35:49.243
You must have done something
to really piss him off.

35:49.320 --> 35:51.832
I assure you this is not
just about Eddie Lane.

35:51.909 --> 35:53.961
In my book, which will be out
in the spring,

35:54.038 --> 35:55.373
I get into the history
of violence

35:55.450 --> 35:56.850
